    "## Per-year view - top 10 tickers, one plot per year\n",
    "\n",
    "Each year gets its **own figure** with that year's top 10 tickers. The\n",
    "inflection threshold (`mean + K x std`) is computed **within the year**, so a\n",
    "ticker's take-off is judged against that year's normal noise - old\n",
    "high-volume years don't drown out newer ones."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 13,
   "id": "cell-7",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stderr",
